name: Tiny House DAO
description:
Tiny house DAO's mission is to promote independent projects, partnerships, and knowledge sharing to facilitate housing affordability, vacation networking, and long term home ownership. 

We are building out a physical network of Tiny Houses and properties, some will DAO owned.
